 \"To the Moon and Back\" (มาตาลดา), he won Best Actor in addition to Best Supporting Actor for his work on \"The Betrayal\" ( เกมรักทรยศ) at the Komchadluek Awards. In June 2024, he won Actor of the Year at the year's 9entertain Awards.\n\nChai is married to actress Vicky Sunisa Jett. The two met on the set of the 2008 TV drama “Phik Tai Kub Bai Khao.” They have two sons; Tristan was born in March 2017 and Tyler was born February 2021. His younger brother Boromwuti Hiranyatithi is also an actor.","name":"Chartayodom Hiranyatithi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ชาตโยดม หิรัญยัติ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"チャタヨドム・ヒラニャティティ","primary":false}}]}},"person_2358823_translations":{"at":1772647235451,"data":{"id":2358823,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jammeh Diangana","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jammeh Diangana","primary":true}}]}}}}